584
00:35:52,900 --> 00:35:59,360
 Ali, evo, brojni autor ističu kako je važno povezivati to, to se zove unutarnje povezivanje kreposti,

585
00:35:59,360 --> 00:36:08,820
 gdje primjerice povezujemo mudrost sa umjerenošću i onda naravno sa pravednošću.

586
00:36:10,820 --> 00:36:15,860
 Jer znamo da imamo još od antike četiri kardinalne ili stožerne kreposti,

587
00:36:15,860 --> 00:36:22,060
 pravednost je jedna od njih, umjerenost je jedna od njih, jakost ili hrabrost je jedna od njih.

588
00:36:22,060 --> 00:36:29,640
 I kad mi povezimo primjerice krepost mudrosti, krepost mudrosti i krepost umjerenosti,

589
00:36:29,640 --> 00:36:33,660
 a to je upravo taj govor o pravoj mjeri, o pravoj mjeri,

590
00:36:33,660 --> 00:36:37,960
 uvijek smo usmjereni, dakle, prema jednoj vrsti pravednosti.

591
00:36:37,960 --> 00:36:42,020
 A što bi bila pravednost, to mi smo rekli već u prethodnim emisijama,

592
00:36:42,020 --> 00:36:47,220
 dati svakome, a to znači samome sebi, ono što čovjeku pripada.

593
00:36:47,220 --> 00:36:50,380
 Ljubi bližnjega svoga kao samoga sebe, a ne?

594
00:36:50,380 --> 00:36:53,200
 Tako je, tako je, tako je, da. Dakle, ono što pripada.

595
00:36:53,200 --> 00:36:56,600
 I sad, naravno, ključno je pitanje u kontekstu govora o krepostima

596
00:36:56,600 --> 00:37:02,640
 i u kontekstu govora o potrebama, koliko je dovoljno.

597
00:37:03,320 --> 00:37:08,200
 Epikur, jedan poznati filozof iz Grčke antike, je rekao da

598
00:37:08,200 --> 00:37:11,840
 one kome dovoljno nije dovoljno, tome ništa nije dovoljno.

599
00:37:11,840 --> 00:37:15,220
 Sad je pitanje, ali koliko je dovoljno onda?

600
00:37:15,220 --> 00:37:20,620
 Dakle, i to je sad, naravno, u srednjem vijeku je bilo potrebno puno manje

601
00:37:20,620 --> 00:37:21,600
 da bude dovoljno.

602
00:37:21,600 --> 00:37:24,660
 Dovoljno, nego danas.

603
00:37:24,660 --> 00:37:28,780
 Nego danas. Grččani u srednjem vijeku su imali puno manje toga što im je bilo potrebno

604
00:37:28,780 --> 00:37:30,660
 nego što to, recimo, mi danas imamo.

605
00:37:30,660 --> 00:37:34,660
 Ali to su i zato što su se pomješale naše želje i potrebe.

606
00:37:34,660 --> 00:37:34,880
 Da.

607
00:37:34,880 --> 00:37:39,900
 I zato što mislimo da su naše želje, u biti, i naše potrebe, ne?

608
00:37:39,900 --> 00:37:46,400
 Pa onda imamo, recimo, da je, evo, želja, ne znam, da djete u osnovnoj školi

609
00:37:46,400 --> 00:37:49,460
 ima jako dobar mobitel, recimo, ne?

610
00:37:49,460 --> 00:37:54,880
 Ili želja da, ne znam, ovaj, djete ima, ne znam, super tenisice.

611
00:37:54,880 --> 00:37:56,900
 Pa naravno da djete treba imati tenisice.

612
00:37:56,900 --> 00:38:00,100
 Ali djete prije svega treba biti djete, a ne?

613
00:38:00,100 --> 00:38:03,020
 Tako da, tu dio.

614
00:38:03,020 --> 00:38:05,160
 Ili kod nas odraslih isto, ovaj.

615
00:38:05,160 --> 00:38:08,540
 Da. I vrijednost nije u onome što čovjek ima.

616
00:38:09,120 --> 00:38:10,540
 nego u onome što je.

617
00:38:10,540 --> 00:38:11,140
 Što je.

618
00:38:11,140 --> 00:38:13,900
 A to ono što kršćani zaista onda unose u ovaj svijet.

619
00:38:13,900 --> 00:38:20,660
 Dakle, to je nešto što je, što je izrazito, možemo reći, i potrebno ovome svijetu.

620
00:38:20,660 --> 00:38:23,760
 Tako da, to pitanje je dovoljnoga.

621
00:38:23,760 --> 00:38:24,620
 Koliko je dovoljno?

622
00:38:24,620 --> 00:38:32,320
 Evo, kada promatramo kreposti, a kreposti, znamo da, dakle, u kršćanstvu su one doživjela svoj procvat

623
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:36,180
 kao jedna čvrsta i postojana odlučnost.

624
00:38:36,180 --> 00:38:38,340
 Dakle, krepost nije nešto što je sad čovjek

625
00:38:38,340 --> 00:38:42,640
 čovjek provodi na temelju svojih osjećaja,

626
00:38:42,640 --> 00:38:44,880
 primjerice kreposti umjerenosti,

627
00:38:44,880 --> 00:38:46,820
 nego je to jedno stanje odlučnosti.

628
00:38:46,820 --> 00:38:49,540
 Dakle, tu smo opet u području razuma,

629
00:38:49,540 --> 00:38:51,020
 opet smo u području slobode,

630
00:38:51,020 --> 00:38:53,080
 gdje čovjek donosi odluku,

631
00:38:53,080 --> 00:38:55,000
 želim biti umjeren,

632
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:58,880
 čak i ako mi se to tako ne da ovaj dan,

633
00:38:58,880 --> 00:39:01,720
 ili ako mi osjećaj govore nešto sasvim drugo.

634
00:39:01,720 --> 00:39:03,620
 Dakle, tu se osjećaju i podlažu razumu

635
00:39:03,620 --> 00:39:06,600
 koji je u svrhu stvarenja veće slobode za čovjeka.

636
00:39:06,600 --> 00:39:12,880
 I kada onda u tom suočavanju sa koliko je dovoljno i regulacije vlastitih potreba,

637
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:16,620
 onda ne ovih samo elementarnih, nego ovih gdje su još i želje uključene,

638
00:39:16,620 --> 00:39:19,980
 onda se mogu jako lijepo kombinirati kreposti mudrosti

639
00:39:19,980 --> 00:39:22,020
 i krepost umjerenosti i pravednosti,

640
00:39:22,020 --> 00:39:25,580
 dakle, i prema samome sebi da se ostvari ono što je najbolje za osobu,

641
00:39:25,580 --> 00:39:29,660
 ali automatski, dakle, svaki individualan čin ima i društvenu posljedicu.

642
00:39:29,660 --> 00:39:32,980
 To je bez sumnje pogađa ili naše najbližnje,

643
00:39:32,980 --> 00:39:37,480
 a i kroz poziciju u društvu puno širi opseg ljudi.

644
00:39:37,480 --> 00:39:41,420
 Da, zato što upravo ovo već smo spomenuli danas par puta,

645
00:39:41,420 --> 00:39:46,740
 da mi nismo sami za sebe ili da mi nismo otok,

646
00:39:46,740 --> 00:39:49,160
 nego da smo mi zajednica, mi smo dio društva,

647
00:39:49,160 --> 00:39:55,040
 svaka obitelj čini dio neke zajednice, dio grada, dio države

648
00:39:55,040 --> 00:39:57,740
 i svaki pojedinac čini tu obitelj.

649
00:39:57,740 --> 00:40:01,740
 Tako da, upravo su ti važni odnosi

650
00:40:01,740 --> 00:40:06,080
 i da ubiti svaki dan gledamo te odnose,

651
00:40:06,080 --> 00:40:08,980
 kakvi su nam ti odnose, i ne samo prema ljudima,

652
00:40:08,980 --> 00:40:12,720
 nego i prema, pa i unutar posla, pa i unutar prijatelja,

653
00:40:13,860 --> 00:40:18,600
 obiteljstva, unutar neke druge zajednice, organizacije,

654
00:40:18,600 --> 00:40:25,980
 unutar, evo, i sad tu isto, jako su važni odnosi međusobno.

655
00:40:25,980 --> 00:40:27,700
 Absolutno, da.

656
00:40:27,700 --> 00:40:31,480
 I ta prava mjera, i onda ta prava mjera,

657
00:40:31,480 --> 00:40:34,300
 kad znamo te male stvari, kako se kaže u Bibliji,

658
00:40:34,300 --> 00:40:36,760
 ko je u malome vjeran i u velikome će biti,

659
00:40:36,760 --> 00:40:39,600
 kad znamo te male stvari, onda ćemo,

660
00:40:39,600 --> 00:40:43,220
 kad to vježbamo svaki dan, onda će nam to svaki dan

661
00:40:43,220 --> 00:40:46,240
 postati nešto normalno, navika,

662
00:40:46,240 --> 00:40:50,260
 i onda ćemo u biti znati za veće stvari

663
00:40:50,260 --> 00:40:54,540
 odlučivati, razbori to,

664
00:40:54,540 --> 00:40:59,260
 razbori to što je prava mjera i što ne.

665
00:40:59,500 --> 00:41:01,560
 A, naravno, pogotovo neko ko je, recimo,

666
00:41:01,560 --> 00:41:03,820
 vlasnik nekog poduzeća,

667
00:41:03,820 --> 00:41:07,140
 pa će znati, ovaj, reći da li treba, evo,

668
00:41:07,140 --> 00:41:09,060
 novac usmjeriti tamo,

669
00:41:09,060 --> 00:41:12,000
 ili novac treba usmjeriti u nekom drugom smjeru,

670
00:41:12,000 --> 00:41:15,800
 ili, evo, stvarno, ovaj,

671
00:41:15,800 --> 00:41:18,540
 evo, i danas, evo, baš sam u novinama čitala,

672
00:41:18,540 --> 00:41:21,960
 je primjer našeg Baby Lazanje,

673
00:41:22,380 --> 00:41:24,400
 vlada mu je darovala 50.000 evora

674
00:41:24,400 --> 00:41:26,980
 i on je automatski, evo, već odlučio

675
00:41:26,980 --> 00:41:29,560
 da tih 50.000 evora želi darovat

676
00:41:29,560 --> 00:41:32,420
 bolnicama, evo, za djecu.

677
00:41:32,420 --> 00:41:35,300
 Koliko je to, recimo, plemeniti jedan čin

678
00:41:35,300 --> 00:41:37,960
 i mogli bi reći njemu sasvim prirodno,

679
00:41:37,960 --> 00:41:41,260
 jer on automatski isti dan odlučio,

680
00:41:41,260 --> 00:41:44,140
 a to je u biti vježbanje,

681
00:41:44,140 --> 00:41:46,260
 to je vježbanje korak po korak,

682
00:41:46,260 --> 00:41:47,960
 ne, bi ja rekla,

683
00:41:47,960 --> 00:41:49,260
 to je ta jedna mjera,

684
00:41:50,280 --> 00:41:51,700
 koliko je meni potrebno,

685
00:41:51,700 --> 00:41:53,040
 što ja želim,

686
00:41:53,040 --> 00:41:54,100
 i opet se vraćamo,

687
00:41:54,100 --> 00:41:55,380
 koje je naše poslanje,

688
00:41:55,380 --> 00:41:59,520
 zašto smo mi na ovome svijetu,

689
00:41:59,520 --> 00:42:01,580
 da li smo mi na ovome svijetu,

690
00:42:01,580 --> 00:42:02,800
 evo, da samo uživamo,

691
00:42:02,800 --> 00:42:07,400
 da stvorimo neku manju zajednicu,

692
00:42:07,400 --> 00:42:11,260
 ili mi imamo neko veće poslanje

693
00:42:11,260 --> 00:42:12,640
 da sa tom zajednicom,

694
00:42:12,640 --> 00:42:14,540
 s tom obitelji koju stvaramo,

695
00:42:14,540 --> 00:42:16,580
 da djelujemo dalje

696
00:42:16,580 --> 00:42:18,160
 i da to dalje širimo

697
00:42:18,160 --> 00:42:20,020
 kršćanske vrijednosti, evo.

698
00:42:20,180 --> 00:42:20,800
 Da, da.

699
00:42:20,800 --> 00:42:23,800
 Da, da, to je u biti kršćanstva,

700
00:42:23,800 --> 00:42:25,240
 zapravo i bogatstvo,

701
00:42:25,240 --> 00:42:28,660
 ako imamo određeni uspjeh,

702
00:42:28,660 --> 00:42:29,280
 dakle,

703
00:42:29,280 --> 00:42:32,180
 kršćanska, dakle,

704
00:42:32,180 --> 00:42:33,280
 i etika i socijalni,

705
00:42:33,280 --> 00:42:34,780
 i taj socijalna dimenzija kršćanstva

706
00:42:34,780 --> 00:42:35,640
 uvijek govori, naravno,

707
00:42:35,640 --> 00:42:37,680
 potrebno je namiriti vlastite potrebe,

708
00:42:37,680 --> 00:42:39,200
 ali svrha i cilj bogatstva

709
00:42:39,200 --> 00:42:41,200
 je blagoslov drugih,

710
00:42:41,200 --> 00:42:44,200
 dakle, da kada smo mi blagoslovljeni,

711
00:42:44,200 --> 00:42:45,740
 određeni materijalnim dobrima,

712
00:42:45,740 --> 00:42:47,240
 to je zaista kršćanski stav,

713
00:42:47,240 --> 00:42:50,080
 onda to ne držimo grčevito za sebe,

714
00:42:50,080 --> 00:42:52,880
 i ne gradimo zidove

715
00:42:52,880 --> 00:42:56,200
 oko svojih hacijenda

716
00:42:56,200 --> 00:42:58,260
 ili ne znam kakvih posjeda,

717
00:42:58,260 --> 00:42:58,860
 dakle,

718
00:42:58,860 --> 00:43:00,240
 kao što je primjerice,

719
00:43:00,240 --> 00:43:02,780
 o to Papa Franju često spominje,

720
00:43:02,780 --> 00:43:04,700
 taj slučaj u Latinskoj Americi,

721
00:43:04,700 --> 00:43:05,840
 gdje se onda,

722
00:43:06,120 --> 00:43:08,500
 imamo izrazito jako bogate ljude,

723
00:43:08,500 --> 00:43:11,620
 koji grade te svoje velike posjede,

724
00:43:11,620 --> 00:43:13,540
 koji su maksimalno osigurani,

725
00:43:13,540 --> 00:43:15,500
 i onda nedaleko od takvih

726
00:43:15,500 --> 00:43:17,700
 neslučajnih razmjera bogatstva,

727
00:43:17,700 --> 00:43:19,680
 imamo ljude koji žive u velikoj bjedi,

728
00:43:19,680 --> 00:43:20,320
 ne u velikoj,

729
00:43:20,320 --> 00:43:21,780
 nego u nezamislivoj bjedi.

730
00:43:22,660 --> 00:43:24,040
 Dakle, svrha i cilj bogatstva

731
00:43:24,040 --> 00:43:25,700
 nije to ozgrtati ga za sebe

732
00:43:25,700 --> 00:43:27,020
 i čuvati grčevito,

733
00:43:27,020 --> 00:43:29,360
 nego je svrha i cilj bogatstva

734
00:43:29,360 --> 00:43:30,980
 u krčanskoj perspektivi

735
00:43:30,980 --> 00:43:33,920
 blagoslov drugih.

736
00:43:34,640 --> 00:43:36,020
 kao što je ovaj primjer

737
00:43:36,020 --> 00:43:36,900
 koji si navjela,

738
00:43:36,900 --> 00:43:38,260
 jer to je,

739
00:43:38,260 --> 00:43:40,200
 ako gledamo Evanđelja,

740
00:43:40,200 --> 00:43:41,880
 Isus Hristo konstantno kaže

741
00:43:41,880 --> 00:43:47,980
 da ne možemo služiti dvojci gospodara,

742
00:43:47,980 --> 00:43:49,680
 ne možemo služiti Bogu i novcu.

743
00:43:49,680 --> 00:43:51,840
 Dakle, novac je taj koji

744
00:43:51,840 --> 00:43:54,400
 nije naš gospodar

745
00:43:54,400 --> 00:43:58,240
 u smislu da on čovjekov život usmjeruje,

746
00:43:58,240 --> 00:44:00,500
 nego je čovjek taj koji usmjeruje novac.

747
00:44:00,500 --> 00:44:04,460
 I zato Isus Hristo ima jako lijepih citata

748
00:44:04,460 --> 00:44:07,220
 iz Evanđelja koji se sučava

749
00:44:07,220 --> 00:44:09,540
 i sa vrlo konkretnom ekonomskom tematikom.

750
00:44:09,540 --> 00:44:12,000
 To je bilo zanimljivo isto proučavati,

751
00:44:12,000 --> 00:44:14,520
 gdje dobivamo jasne smjernice

752
00:44:14,520 --> 00:44:16,120
 u odnosu prema bogatstvu,

753
00:44:16,120 --> 00:44:18,160
 prema novcu i odgovor na pitanje

754
00:44:18,160 --> 00:44:19,900
 zapravo što je pravo bogatstvo.

755
00:44:19,900 --> 00:44:22,100
 Da li je pravo bogatstvo imati puno novaca?

756
00:44:22,100 --> 00:44:26,960
 Ili je bogatstvo negdje drugdje?

757
00:44:26,960 --> 00:44:29,340
 Papa Franjo također kaže

758
00:44:29,340 --> 00:44:30,920
 da je neki od naj...

759
00:44:30,920 --> 00:44:33,040
 Ako bogatstvo često vezujemo

760
00:44:33,040 --> 00:44:34,000
 uz koncept sreće,

761
00:44:34,080 --> 00:44:35,640
 bit ćemo sretnije ako smo bogati.

762
00:44:35,640 --> 00:44:36,960
 A Papa Franjo kaže

763
00:44:36,960 --> 00:44:42,140
 ne, ja sam najskrenije iskustva sreće

764
00:44:42,140 --> 00:44:44,640
 vidio na licima najsiromašnijih ljudi.

765
00:44:44,640 --> 00:44:48,200
 I sad kaže on to u Apostolskoj pobodnici

766
00:44:48,200 --> 00:44:49,120
 Evangelii Gaudium,

767
00:44:49,120 --> 00:44:50,060
 radost evanđelja.

768
00:44:50,060 --> 00:44:51,440
 I naravno sad se možemo zapitati

769
00:44:51,440 --> 00:44:52,200
 kako, kako?

770
00:44:52,200 --> 00:44:53,660
 Kod najsiromašnijih.

771
00:44:53,660 --> 00:44:55,720
 A on kaže zato jer se oni nemaju

772
00:44:55,720 --> 00:44:56,880
 na što navezati.

773
00:44:56,880 --> 00:44:59,560
 Dakle, to je nema ih što vezati,

774
00:44:59,560 --> 00:45:00,700
 a s druge strane

775
00:45:00,700 --> 00:45:02,360
 onda imaju jedni druge

776
00:45:02,360 --> 00:45:03,620
 kao najveće bogatstvo.

777
00:45:03,700 --> 00:45:05,040
 Imaju jedne druge.

778
00:45:05,040 --> 00:45:07,900
 Upravo se o tome razmišljano.

779
00:45:07,900 --> 00:45:10,120
 Što smo rekli u prošloj emisiji,

780
00:45:10,120 --> 00:45:12,640
 nije novac problemi,

781
00:45:12,640 --> 00:45:14,860
 nije novac neko zlo.

782
00:45:14,860 --> 00:45:16,280
 Novac je samo sredstvo.

783
00:45:16,280 --> 00:45:18,520
 Sredstvo kako ćemo mi njega

784
00:45:18,520 --> 00:45:19,940
 upotrijebiti

785
00:45:19,940 --> 00:45:21,800
 ili u kojem smjeru ćemo mi njega

786
00:45:21,800 --> 00:45:22,660
 usmjeriti.

787
00:45:23,160 --> 00:45:25,200
 za što ćemo ga usmjeriti.

788
00:45:25,200 --> 00:45:29,900
 Tako da, naravno da mi ekonomisti,

789
00:45:29,900 --> 00:45:33,500
 pogotovo mi koji se bavimo sa poduzetništvom,

790
00:45:33,500 --> 00:45:36,380
 naravno da se stvara profita.

791
00:45:36,500 --> 00:45:37,740
 Pitanje je, znači,

792
00:45:37,740 --> 00:45:39,560
 kako ćemo mi taj profit

793
00:45:39,560 --> 00:45:42,700
 usmjeriti dalje.

794
00:45:42,700 --> 00:45:44,840
 Da li će to biti, evo,

795
00:45:44,840 --> 00:45:47,440
 za neke želje

796
00:45:47,440 --> 00:45:50,120
 ili će biti za boljitak,

797
00:45:50,120 --> 00:45:51,020
 recimo, društva.

798
00:45:51,020 --> 00:45:52,780
 Naravno da mi tu imamo slobodi,

799
00:45:52,780 --> 00:45:54,060
 evo, cijelo vrijeme i o tome

800
00:45:54,060 --> 00:45:56,120
 pričamo, ali

801
00:45:56,120 --> 00:45:57,940
 što je to što će nama doniti

802
00:45:57,940 --> 00:45:59,020
 zadovoljstvo?

803
00:45:59,240 --> 00:46:01,460
 Ne vanjsku neku, eto,

804
00:46:01,460 --> 00:46:02,560
 osmijeh, radost,

805
00:46:02,560 --> 00:46:04,080
 nego unutarnje zadovoljstvo,

806
00:46:04,080 --> 00:46:05,240
 zadovoljstvo koje će biti

807
00:46:05,240 --> 00:46:06,040
 unutar nas, a ne.

808
00:46:06,040 --> 00:46:07,520
 Za to smo mi kršćani,

809
00:46:07,520 --> 00:46:09,220
 to su kršćanske neke vrijednosti.

810
00:46:09,220 --> 00:46:11,620
 I naravno da svako ima slobodu birat

811
00:46:11,620 --> 00:46:15,100
 kako će taj novac svoj potrošiti.

812
00:46:15,100 --> 00:46:16,740
 To je neupitno.

813
00:46:16,740 --> 00:46:18,980
 Stvar je samo da,

814
00:46:18,980 --> 00:46:20,540
 ako smo mi kršćani,

815
00:46:20,540 --> 00:46:23,520
 koje vrijednosti mi

816
00:46:23,520 --> 00:46:26,300
 šaljemo u svijet?

817
00:46:27,980 --> 00:46:30,040
 Kako je to naš način,

818
00:46:30,040 --> 00:46:31,080
 stil života

819
00:46:31,080 --> 00:46:33,200
 koji mi pokazujemo

820
00:46:33,200 --> 00:46:34,020
 drugima?

821
00:46:34,020 --> 00:46:36,680
 I evo, to upravo poslanje

822
00:46:36,680 --> 00:46:39,360
 što smo i danas pričali.

823
00:46:39,360 --> 00:46:42,160
 Koje je to naše ovaj poslanje?

824
00:46:42,160 --> 00:46:43,380
 Da li je naše poslanje,

825
00:46:43,380 --> 00:46:45,880
 znači, da ako imamo novac

826
00:46:45,880 --> 00:46:46,720
 s tim novcem,

827
00:46:46,720 --> 00:46:49,760
 drugoga razveseliti,

828
00:46:49,760 --> 00:46:52,120
 drugome omogućiti

829
00:46:52,120 --> 00:46:53,860
 još bolji neki odnos,

830
00:46:53,860 --> 00:46:54,740
 bolji život?

831
00:46:56,720 --> 00:47:00,280
 Ili nešto drugo.

832
00:47:00,280 --> 00:47:01,840
 Koje je to mjera?

833
00:47:01,840 --> 00:47:03,420
 Koje je to prava mjera?

834
00:47:03,420 --> 00:47:05,960
 Naravno da nije prava mjera,

835
00:47:05,960 --> 00:47:07,100
 sve dadu drugima.

836
00:47:07,100 --> 00:47:09,240
 Naravno da to nije prava mjera.

837
00:47:09,240 --> 00:47:10,000
 Isus je rekao,

838
00:47:10,000 --> 00:47:12,920
 ljubi druge kao što ljubiš sebe.

839
00:47:12,920 --> 00:47:15,320
 Ljubi Boga iznad svega,

840
00:47:15,320 --> 00:47:17,620
 ali moraš ljubiti sebe,

841
00:47:17,620 --> 00:47:20,000
 jer i ti si stvorenje Božje.

842
00:47:20,000 --> 00:47:21,460
 I tebe Bog ljubi.

843
00:47:21,780 --> 00:47:25,040
 I Bog želi da se svako od nas ostvari

844
00:47:25,040 --> 00:47:26,820
 i da upunini, upunini.

845
00:47:26,820 --> 00:47:27,820
 I to je Božja volja,

846
00:47:27,820 --> 00:47:28,840
 da budemo sretni,

847
00:47:28,840 --> 00:47:30,740
 da budemo ispunjeni,

848
00:47:30,740 --> 00:47:33,380
 da budemo zadovoljni.

849
00:47:33,380 --> 00:47:34,920
 Marijana,

850
00:47:34,920 --> 00:47:38,220
 evo prošlo je naših sat vremena.

851
00:47:38,220 --> 00:47:39,080
 molim te,

852
00:47:39,080 --> 00:47:41,760
 par rečenica ako želiš za kraj

853
00:47:41,760 --> 00:47:43,360
 reći možda.

854
00:47:43,360 --> 00:47:46,260
 Da, evo,

855
00:47:46,260 --> 00:47:48,600
 kršćanska perspektiva i pogled

856
00:47:48,600 --> 00:47:51,300
 na život ovome svijetu

857
00:47:51,300 --> 00:47:52,960
 je zaista vrlo nadahnjujuća.

858
00:47:52,960 --> 00:47:54,020
 Evo,

859
00:47:54,020 --> 00:47:56,140
 i kaže Papa Franjo

860
00:47:56,140 --> 00:47:58,080
 u Evangeliji Gaudium

861
00:47:58,080 --> 00:47:58,780
 radost evančeva,

862
00:47:58,780 --> 00:48:00,560
 to je naprednje naposloska pobodnica.

863
00:48:00,560 --> 00:48:02,380
 Ko bi mogla zatvoriti

864
00:48:02,380 --> 00:48:03,220
 svetog Franju,

865
00:48:03,220 --> 00:48:04,900
 Asiškoga ili svetu Tereziju

866
00:48:04,900 --> 00:48:05,600
 kao kutu

867
00:48:05,600 --> 00:48:08,120
 u neku prostoriju

868
00:48:08,120 --> 00:48:09,420
 iz koje oni ne bi mogli

869
00:48:09,420 --> 00:48:10,800
 djelovati u svijetu.

870
00:48:10,800 --> 00:48:11,080
 Dakle,

871
00:48:11,080 --> 00:48:12,520
 nitko ne bi mogao

872
00:48:12,520 --> 00:48:14,800
 istinske, autentične kršćane

873
00:48:14,800 --> 00:48:15,960
 sakriti od svijeta,

874
00:48:15,960 --> 00:48:17,000
 recimo to tako.

875
00:48:17,000 --> 00:48:18,980
 Oni su

876
00:48:18,980 --> 00:48:20,200
 u toj svijesti

877
00:48:20,200 --> 00:48:21,500
 vlastitog identiteta,

878
00:48:21,500 --> 00:48:22,180
 a prije svega

879
00:48:22,180 --> 00:48:23,280
 u odnosa s Bogom

880
00:48:23,280 --> 00:48:24,640
 kojeg imaju,

881
00:48:24,640 --> 00:48:25,520
 iz kojeg dobivaju

882
00:48:25,520 --> 00:48:26,660
 svoj vlastit identitet,

883
00:48:26,660 --> 00:48:27,500
 zaista mogli

884
00:48:27,500 --> 00:48:28,580
 djelovati

885
00:48:28,580 --> 00:48:31,620
 ne samo u društvu

886
00:48:31,620 --> 00:48:33,600
 i svijetu vremena

887
00:48:33,600 --> 00:48:35,560
 dok su bili na ovoj zemlji,

888
00:48:35,600 --> 00:48:37,100
 nego vidimo

889
00:48:37,100 --> 00:48:38,280
 i puno šire

890
00:48:38,280 --> 00:48:39,840
 dakle na cijelu povijest.

891
00:48:39,840 --> 00:48:40,920
 Mi ih se svi sjećamo

892
00:48:40,920 --> 00:48:42,680
 i velika su nam inspiracija.

893
00:48:42,680 --> 00:48:43,480
 Ali

894
00:48:43,480 --> 00:48:46,440
 to ne znači da postoji

895
00:48:46,440 --> 00:48:47,460
 samo nekoliko ljudi

896
00:48:47,460 --> 00:48:48,320
 na povijesti

897
00:48:48,320 --> 00:48:49,480
 koji to mogu ostvariti.

898
00:48:49,480 --> 00:48:49,960
 To je nešto

899
00:48:49,960 --> 00:48:51,160
 što je svima nama

900
00:48:51,160 --> 00:48:52,260
 i tekako

901
00:48:52,260 --> 00:48:53,380
 moguće.

902
00:48:53,380 --> 00:48:54,740
 Zato imamo te

903
00:48:54,740 --> 00:48:55,540
 najograničenije

904
00:48:55,540 --> 00:48:56,180
 resurse,

905
00:48:56,180 --> 00:48:56,740
 vrijeme

906
00:48:56,740 --> 00:48:58,040
 na ovome svijetu

907
00:48:58,040 --> 00:48:59,020
 koje nam je dano

908
00:48:59,020 --> 00:49:00,100
 da ostvarimo

909
00:49:00,100 --> 00:49:00,740
 taj cilj,

910
00:49:00,740 --> 00:49:01,700
 a svetost,

911
00:49:01,700 --> 00:49:02,020
 evo,

912
00:49:02,020 --> 00:49:03,440
 da zaključimo sa time,

913
00:49:03,440 --> 00:49:04,560
 svetost zaista

914
00:49:04,560 --> 00:49:05,460
 je stajna

915
00:49:05,460 --> 00:49:07,080
 kršćanskog bivanja

916
00:49:07,080 --> 00:49:07,980
 u svijetu,

917
00:49:07,980 --> 00:49:09,540
 ali ne od svijeta,

918
00:49:09,540 --> 00:49:11,080
 jer svetost,

919
00:49:11,080 --> 00:49:12,440
 ako uzemo latinsku riječ

920
00:49:12,440 --> 00:49:13,420
 sanctus,

921
00:49:13,420 --> 00:49:15,160
 to je latinska riječ

922
00:49:15,160 --> 00:49:15,700
 za svet,

923
00:49:15,700 --> 00:49:16,380
 sanctus

924
00:49:16,380 --> 00:49:17,420
 dolazi od riječi

925
00:49:17,420 --> 00:49:18,040
 sanus,

926
00:49:18,040 --> 00:49:19,000
 što znači zdrav.

927
00:49:19,660 --> 00:49:19,920
 Dakle,

928
00:49:19,920 --> 00:49:20,860
 svet čovjek je onaj

929
00:49:20,860 --> 00:49:21,640
 koje je zdrav.

930
00:49:21,640 --> 00:49:24,180
 Odlično.

931
00:49:24,180 --> 00:49:24,660
 I to nije nešto

932
00:49:24,660 --> 00:49:25,400
 što je sad

933
00:49:25,400 --> 00:49:26,400
 privilegija

934
00:49:26,400 --> 00:49:28,000
 samo četvero

935
00:49:28,000 --> 00:49:30,000
 crkvenih naučitelja.

936
00:49:30,000 --> 00:49:30,820
 Upravo to razmišljam,

937
00:49:30,820 --> 00:49:31,100
 da.

938
00:49:31,100 --> 00:49:32,880
 Bit svet

939
00:49:32,880 --> 00:49:33,620
 to je

940
00:49:33,620 --> 00:49:34,900
 poslanje svih nas,

941
00:49:34,900 --> 00:49:35,720
 a evo,

942
00:49:35,720 --> 00:49:36,620
 baš mi se sviđa

943
00:49:36,620 --> 00:49:37,440
 ovo kako si rekla

944
00:49:37,440 --> 00:49:38,120
 i s tim bih volila

945
00:49:38,120 --> 00:49:38,720
 i završiti.

946
00:49:38,720 --> 00:49:39,780
 Bit svet

947
00:49:39,780 --> 00:49:40,220
 znači

948
00:49:40,220 --> 00:49:40,920
 bit zdrav.

949
00:49:40,920 --> 00:49:42,220
 Bit svet

950
00:49:42,220 --> 00:49:43,620
 nije neka privilegija,

951
00:49:43,620 --> 00:49:44,420
 ponovit ćemo,

952
00:49:44,420 --> 00:49:45,940
 nego to je nešto

953
00:49:45,940 --> 00:49:46,440
 što

954
00:49:46,440 --> 00:49:47,940
 Bog traži

955
00:49:47,940 --> 00:49:49,360
 od svih nas.

956
00:49:49,660 --> 00:49:51,460
 zato što mi to možemo

957
00:49:51,460 --> 00:49:52,440
 na nama,

958
00:49:52,440 --> 00:49:52,720
 evo,

959
00:49:52,720 --> 00:49:53,180
 da se

960
00:49:53,180 --> 00:49:54,900
 za to odlučimo

961
00:49:54,900 --> 00:49:56,620
 i da težimo tome.

962
00:49:56,620 --> 00:49:57,320
 To nije nešto

963
00:49:57,320 --> 00:49:58,440
 što možemo

964
00:49:58,440 --> 00:49:59,400
 biti jedan dan

965
00:49:59,400 --> 00:50:00,620
 niti postati sveti

966
00:50:00,620 --> 00:50:02,820
 u 24 sata,

967
00:50:02,820 --> 00:50:04,000
