970
00:50:05,800 --> 00:50:06,500
 kroz naš

971
00:50:06,500 --> 00:50:07,740
 životni put

972
00:50:07,740 --> 00:50:09,680
 se truditi

973
00:50:09,680 --> 00:50:10,500
 biti sveti.

974
00:50:10,500 --> 00:50:11,420
 Evo,

975
00:50:11,420 --> 00:50:12,400
