976
00:50:12,400 --> 00:50:13,620
 hvala ti još

977
00:50:13,620 --> 00:50:14,260
 jedan put

978
00:50:14,260 --> 00:50:15,600
 na ovoj emisiji.

979
00:50:15,600 --> 00:50:16,280
 Bilo mi je

980
00:50:16,280 --> 00:50:17,380
