981
00:50:17,380 --> 00:50:18,200
 jako lijepo

982
00:50:18,200 --> 00:50:19,400
 razgovarati.

983
00:50:19,660 --> 00:50:21,220
 dragi slušatelji,

984
00:50:21,220 --> 00:50:22,300
 dragi gledatelji,

985
00:50:22,300 --> 00:50:24,020
 hvala i vama.

986
00:50:24,020 --> 00:50:25,540
 Na, evo,

987
00:50:25,540 --> 00:50:26,700
 ovom zajedničkom

988
00:50:26,700 --> 00:50:27,900
 provedenom vremenu,

989
00:50:27,900 --> 00:50:29,040
 moje ime je

990
00:50:29,040 --> 00:50:30,580
 Katarina Buksa,

991
00:50:30,580 --> 00:50:31,720
 ja sam urednica

992
00:50:31,720 --> 00:50:32,800
 i voditeljica

993
00:50:32,800 --> 00:50:33,400
