994
00:50:33,400 --> 00:50:34,880
 Franjine ekonomije.

995
00:50:34,880 --> 00:50:36,180
 Danas nam je

996
00:50:36,180 --> 00:50:37,080
 tehnički urednik

997
00:50:37,080 --> 00:50:38,220
 bio gospodin Ivan

998
00:50:38,220 --> 00:50:39,320
